"Wird is an integrated digital platform that aims to facilitate the "
"recitation and contemplation of the Quran in an organized and attractive "
"way. It provides services such as browsing various Mushafs, listening to "
"reciters, and reading authentic Tafsir books."

msgid "about_wird"
msgstr ""
"Wird is an integrated digital platform that aims to facilitate the "
"recitation and contemplation of the Quran in an organized and attractive "
"way. It offers services such as browsing Mushafs with various narrations, "
"listening to reciters, and reading reliable Tafsirs. It also allows users to "
"follow their daily Wird and track their progress in memorization and "
"revision. The platform aims to support the Quran project and strengthen the "
"connection with it through an easy and integrated digital experience."

